# 📦 Borrowing System (Full-Stack Web App)

A full-stack web application for managing item borrowing and returning with authentication and role-based access control.

---

## 🚀 Features

### 👤 User

- Register & Login (JWT Authentication)
- View available items
- Borrow items
- Return items

### 🛠️ Admin

- Add / Edit / Delete items
- View all borrowing records

---

## 🧑‍💻 Tech Stack

### Frontend

- React.js
- Axios
- React Router

### Backend

- Node.js
- Express.js
- MySQL
- JWT (jsonwebtoken)
- bcryptjs

---

